First we need to create the 


::: {.cell}

```{.r .cell-code .hidden}
genes <- paste("gene",1:1000,sep="")
set.seed(20231214)
x <- list(A=sample(genes,300),
          B=sample(genes,525),
          C=sample(genes,440),
          D=sample(genes,350))
```
:::


Create spatial plot:


::: {#cell-fig-venn .cell}

```{.r .cell-code .hidden}
#| label: fig-venn
#| fig-cap: "Venn diagram for qualitative analysis/overview of the fancy maths things"
#| fig-alt: "TODO"
ggVennDiagram(x) + 
  scale_fill_gradient(low="grey90",
                      high = "red")
```
